de.fhb.sailboat.ufer.prototyp

Class BoatMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhb.sailboat.ufer.prototyp.BoatMonitor

  • public class BoatMonitor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a monitor for viewing and checking data send by/ concerning the sailboat. After choosing the type of data to be displayed it provides a panel for adding to the main user interface. Such a data view is called a "perspective" within this class.
    Author:
    Patrick Rutter
